com.ti.dvt.engine.scripting

Class ScriptAnalysisSession

  • java.lang.Object
    • ScriptSession
      • com.ti.dvt.engine.scripting.ScriptAnalysisSession
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.beans.ExceptionListener

    public class ScriptAnalysisSession
extends ScriptSession
implements java.beans.ExceptionListener
    A wrapper class for scripting Analysis Configurations.
    Typical usage:
    analysisSession = dvtServer.openAnalysisSession();
    ...
    analysis = analysisSession.loadAnalysis("_analysisName_");
    analysis.setProperty("_propertyName_", value);
    ...
    analysis.setProperty("_propertyName_", value);
    analysis.run();
    ...
    analyzer = analysis.findAnalyzerByName("_analyzerName_");
    analyzer.waitForEndOfData();
    ...
    analyzer.exportDataToCSV("_dataTableName_", "_fileName_", "_listOfFields_");
    ...
    analysisSession.endAnalysis(analysis);
